---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: 'Stefan Taitano'
description: 'ServiceNow Developer & Consultant, Veteran, and Chess Enthusiast based in Minneapolis, MN.'
articles:
  title: 'Recent Articles'
  intro: 'A few things I have written lately.'
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-light);">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>
    {% svg "divider/waves", null, "divider" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-xl); align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">

        <figure aria-label="Stefan Taitano" style="flex-shrink: 0; inline-size: min(220px, 100%); aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden;">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/stefan.png"
            alt="Stefan Taitano"
            width="220"
            height="220"
            style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 20%;"
          >
        </figure>

        <div class="flow" style="flex: 1; min-inline-size: 25ch;">
          <p style="font-size: var(--step-1); font-style: italic;">I build systems for a living and escape plans for fun.</p>
          <p>
            I'm Stefan — a ServiceNow Developer &amp; Consultant at Cognizant, based in Minneapolis, MN.
            On the side, I'm deep in a backend development arc with <a href="https://www.boot.dev/u/chessboot">boot.dev</a>
            and slowly dabbling in a variety of games.
          </p>
          <p>
            Find me on
            <a href="https://github.com/stefanintech">GitHub</a>,
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefantaitano/">LinkedIn</a>, and
            <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/stefantaitano.com">Bluesky</a>.
            Want to know what I'm focused on right now? Check the <a href="/now/">Now page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="prose wrapper flow">
      <h2>{{ articles.title }}</h2>
      {% if articles.intro %}
        <p>{{ articles.intro }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="feature | region region-space-l">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          {% set itemList = collections.allPosts %}
          {% asyncEach item in itemList.slice(0, 4) %}
            {% set headingLevel = "h3" %}
            {% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}
          {% endeach %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
